  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  AHI more than 15

          -  Friedmans stage I and II

          -  Tonsil size 2, 3 and 4

          -  BMI below 34

          -  Failed use of CPAP and dental device

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe cardiovascular or neurological disease

          -  Prefers strongly one surgical method

          -  ASA IV
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
